| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4248 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 834ad02e-710b-5748-a0fe-74e9edbd7574"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
